    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "The part most people will miss from this paper:\n\nDevelopers who delegated everything to AI scored below 40%. But developers who used AI to ask conceptual questions and understand the code scored above 65%.\n\nSame tool. Completely different outcomes.\n\nThe problem isn’t AI coding.",
